                    <span>Students re-enrolling after 2 (two) years of absence must go through a new application process including payment of all due fees.</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                    <span class="icon-[tabler--ban] text-red-500 size-6 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5"></span>
